<BaseLayout
  title="Pottery & Candle Studio in Centerville, TN | Paint, Create & Relax"
  description="Made @ The Local Place offers pottery painting, candle making, and art classes in Centerville, TN - just 45 minutes from Nashville. No experience needed. Book your creative experience today!"
